attributes.title: Integrity to Time Helps You Mirror Superconsciousness
attributes.description: In this video (23 May, 2017), Paramahamsa Nithyananda reveals how Integrity to time aligns our inner space to superconsciousness. Our inner space is like a mirror & time is a powerful dimension of the cosmos. If we are integrated to time, our inner space aligns to reflect the consciousness in it's complete purity, giving a superconscious breakthrough and ultimately enlightenment itself.
